This is to inform you that ICRA Limited has upgraded the Long Term Bank Facilities ratings and has reaffirmed the Short Term Bank Facilities/ Commercial Paper ratings of the Company as under;
Long term Bank Facilities (Working Capital)/ Debt Instruments: ICRA AA+/Stable (Double A Plus Outlook Stable).

Short Term Bank Facilities (Working Capital/ Commercial Paper): ICRA A1+ (A One Plus)
